long.ar:
ChatGPT with Youtube videos summary generator provides an access to the summary of YouTube videos. Let you quickly get the content of the YouTube video, save time and learn quicker. Relying on ChatGPT artificial intelligence, it will achieve effective re-creation.In addition,you can also easily copy information on both YouTube and chat.openai.com pages.

Features
● Save time:Quickly go to Youtube video location in the transcript
● Fast speed:Load quickly to videos summary
● Easy to use:Copy the transcript and summary with one click

How to use
● Simply go to YouTube website
● Choose the video you are interested in
● Click the Transcript &summary button.It will show you the video transcript, if it has.
● Click the View AI Summary Icon, If you already logged in chat.openai.com, we will get the video summary.
● Click the Copy Icon,then you easily get the summary of YT video.

🙋FAQ:
👉  Do you upgrade/modify the extension?
Yes, we do! In fact, at this very moment, we’re working on features that are probably going to be added. We have a goal of making ChatGPT for YouTube Video Summary the best ChatGPT extension out there, and we take this mission very seriously.We strive to keep up with the fast-paced development of ChatGPT to bring you the best possible experience.
👉  How do I install ChatGPT For YouTube in my browser ?
To install ChatGPT For YouTube on your browser, you will need to follow these steps:
1) In your browser open the browser's app store or extension store
2) Search for the ChatGPT For YouTube extension in the browser's app store or extension store (or click for : Google Chrome | Mozilla Firefox | edge)
3) Click on the "Add to Browser" or "Install" button to begin the installation process.
4) Follow the prompts to give the extension permission to access certain parts of your browser, if prompted.
👉  Are all of the features totally free to use?
Our extension is currently free and we are trying to always have one version of service that is free. But we would have to put in a small paywall in order to sustain the service. We have plans to do so in the coming weeks. With the paid service you can have faster service, without daily limits and high priority customer support. We aim to best serve you in a model that is most affordable to you.

ChatGPT with Youtube videos summary generator provides an access to the summary of YouTube videos. Let you quickly get the content of the YouTube video, save time and learn quicker. Relying on ChatGPT artificial intelligence, it will achieve effective re-creation.In addition,you can also easily copy information on both YouTube and chat.openai.com pages.

Features
● Save time:Quickly go to Youtube video location in the transcript
● Fast speed:Load quickly to videos summary
● Easy to use:Copy the transcript and summary with one click

How to use
● Simply go to YouTube website
● Choose the video you are interested in
● Click the Transcript &summary button.It will show you the video transcript, if it has.
● Click the View AI Summary Icon, If you already logged in chat.openai.com, we will get the video summary.
● Click the Copy Icon,then you easily get the summary of YT video.

Q&A
Q1:What is ChatGPT?
A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. With its diverse range of training on internet text, ChatGPT can provide responses on various topics, such as general knowledge, conversations, and creative writing.

Q2:What is Youtube video summary?
A2:YouTube video summary is a written overview of the content in a video on the YouTube platform. The summary provides a quick way to understand the video's topic and important information.

Q3:Is YouTube Videos Summary Easy Copy with ChatGPT free?
A3:Although our extension is currently free, we are exploring the possibility of introducing a small paywall to sustain the service in the future. By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
A4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

long.cs:
ChatGPT with Youtube videos summary generator provides an access to the summary of YouTube videos. Let you quickly get the content of the YouTube video, save time and learn quicker. Relying on ChatGPT artificial intelligence, it will achieve effective re-creation.In addition,you can also easily copy information on both YouTube and chat.openai.com pages.

Features
● Save time:Quickly go to Youtube video location in the transcript
● Fast speed:Load quickly to videos summary
● Easy to use:Copy the transcript and summary with one click

How to use
● Simply go to YouTube website
● Choose the video you are interested in
● Click the Transcript &summary button.It will show you the video transcript, if it has.
● Click the View AI Summary Icon, If you already logged in chat.openai.com, we will get the video summary.
● Click the Copy Icon,then you easily get the summary of YT video.

🙋FAQ:
👉  Do you upgrade/modify the extension?
Yes, we do! In fact, at this very moment, we’re working on features that are probably going to be added. We have a goal of making ChatGPT for YouTube Video Summary the best ChatGPT extension out there, and we take this mission very seriously.We strive to keep up with the fast-paced development of ChatGPT to bring you the best possible experience.
👉  How do I install ChatGPT For YouTube in my browser ?
To install ChatGPT For YouTube on your browser, you will need to follow these steps:
1) In your browser open the browser's app store or extension store
2) Search for the ChatGPT For YouTube extension in the browser's app store or extension store (or click for : Google Chrome | Mozilla Firefox | edge)
3) Click on the "Add to Browser" or "Install" button to begin the installation process.
4) Follow the prompts to give the extension permission to access certain parts of your browser, if prompted.
👉  Are all of the features totally free to use?
Our extension is currently free and we are trying to always have one version of service that is free. But we would have to put in a small paywall in order to sustain the service. We have plans to do so in the coming weeks. With the paid service you can have faster service, without daily limits and high priority customer support. We aim to best serve you in a model that is most affordable to you.

long.en,en_AU:
AI YouTube & Web Summary, PDF Summarizer and MindMap Generator powered by ChatGPT & Claude 3.Summarize youtube videos and web articles and easy to notes. Highlight text on any web page to get the best definitions and translations. Key content can also be shared on social media.

NoteGPT AI can provide you with summaries and excerpts of YouTube videos, web articles and PDF, allowing you to quickly access everything on the internet. You can also quickly take screenshots or record timestamped notes while watching videos to help you save time and learn quickly. This tool leverages NoteGPT AI capabilities, allowing you to quickly obtain key information from web content. By highlighting PDF or any important content, you can get definitions and translations, while also providing intelligent AI chat. It supports sharing text to social media.

For more details, please visit our website: https://notegpt.io/, and explore the features at https://notegpt.io/workspace/create.

🎉 Key Features:
● Time-saving: Quickly locate specific points in video transcripts with just one click.
● Insightful: Define your video summary structure freely for a 5-second rapid overview.
● Note Empowerment: Record intelligent notes with timestamps and capture screenshots effortlessly.
● AI Chat: Pose challenging questions to NoteGPT AI about video content and receive in-depth answers.
● Web Summaries: 1-click for a webpage overview summary, with word definition function for precise key point understanding.
● Mind Map: Smartly Generate Editable Mind Maps for Structured Knowledge Expansion.
● AI Translation: Utilizing AI capabilities for authentic translation of subtitles and summaries, breaking language barriers once and for all.
● PDF Summary：Summarize online and local PDFs with our PDF Summarizer for efficient knowledge acquisition. (Try arxiv papers)
● NEW!!! Web/PDF HighLight：Support for web text highlighting, online PDF highlighting, text translation, viewing definitions and key points, and sharing highlighted text to Twitter
● Support for obtaining subtitles and summarizing YouTube videos without captions.


👉🏻 How to Use:
【YouTube Summary】
● Visit the YouTube website.
● Select the video of interest.
● Click on the "Transcript" tab to view the video transcription.
● Navigate to the "Summary" tab for a quick video overview and customize the prompt.
● Visit the "Notes" tab to record timestamped video notes, with the ability to jump to corresponding positions. Effortlessly capture screenshots.
● Click on the "AI Chat" tab to engage in intelligent conversations with NoteGPT AI. Access this page through recommended questions on the "Summary" page.
【Web Summary】
● Click on the NoteGPT floating icon on the right side of any webpage（Including Online PDF）.
● Quickly access the webpage summary, view overview, and related FAQs.
● Highlight words or paragraphs from web pages or online PDFs, view further definitions, translations, highlights, and share key content to Twitter with one click.
● You can freely customize the toggle for webpage summaries in the settings page.
【Mind Map】
● Generate Mind Maps with One Click on the Summary Page.
● Drag, Zoom, and Pan with Ease for Comprehensive Viewing.
● Efficient Editing for Quick Creation, Customization, and Export of Your Mind Maps.
● Transform Text into Visual Thinking, Liberate Your Ideas.
● Download AI Mind Map as PNG, SVG without watermark.

💡 FAQ:
● Q1: What is NoteGPT?
    ● A1: NoteGPT is an intelligent learning assistant designed for various learners. It provides summaries and 5-second overviews of any information from any website, including videos and articles. With AI-driven summaries, notes, and other AI features, it aims to save you 60% of your time.
● Q2: What are YouTube video summaries and web summaries（Including Online PDF）?
    ● A2: A YouTube video summary is a brief overview of the content of a video on the YouTube platform; a web summary（Including PDF Summary） provides key points and an overview of the text on a webpage. Summaries offer a quick way to understand the video's topic and important information.
● Q3: Is NoteGPT: YouTube & Web Summary with ChatGPT free?
    ● A3: NoteGPT AI services are free with limited usage. After consuming 15 quotas, consider upgrading to a paid plan for additional quotas and benefits such as stability, faster service response, and personalized customer support.
● Q4: Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
    ● A4: No ChatGPT account is required. NoteGPT seamlessly integrates ChatGPT capabilities without the need for a separate account.

Transform your YouTube learning experience with NoteGPT AI! 🚀

💫 Troubleshooting
You can join us through this Discord invitation link: https://discord.gg/wzNfuks8Qk. Alternatively, you can simply click the Discord icon button located in the lower left corner of the plug-in pop-up window to join with a single click. If you prefer, you can also reach out to us via email at our Google email address: notegpt@gmail.com.

long.fr:
ChatGPT avec le générateur de résumé de vidéos Youtube permet d'accéder au résumé des vidéos YouTube. Il vous permet d'obtenir rapidement le contenu de la vidéo YouTube, de gagner du temps et d'apprendre plus rapidement. En outre, vous pouvez également copier facilement des informations sur les pages de YouTube et de chat.openai.com.

Pour plus de détails, vous pouvez visiter notre site Web : https://notegpt.io/youtube-summary-with-chatgpt

Caractéristiques
● Gagner du temps:Aller rapidement à l'emplacement de la vidéo Youtube dans la transcription.
● Rapidité : Chargement rapide du résumé des vidéos
● Facile à utiliser : copiez la transcription et le résumé en un seul clic.

Mode d'emploi
● Allez simplement sur le site web de YouTube
● Choisissez la vidéo qui vous intéresse
● Cliquez sur le bouton Transcript &summary.It vous montrera la transcription de la vidéo, si elle a.
● Cliquez sur l'icône View AI Summary, Si vous êtes déjà connecté à chat.openai.com, nous obtiendrons le résumé de la vidéo.
● Cliquez sur l'icône Copier, puis vous obtenez facilement le résumé de la vidéo YT.

Q&R
Q1:Qu'est-ce que ChatGPT ?
A1:ChatGPT est un modèle de langage développé par OpenAI qui utilise un grand réseau neuronal pré-entraîné basé sur Transformer pour générer un texte semblable à celui d'un humain en réponse aux invites de l'utilisateur. Grâce à sa formation diversifiée sur les textes Internet, ChatGPT peut fournir des réponses sur différents sujets, tels que les connaissances générales, les conversations et l'écriture créative.

Q2:Qu'est-ce qu'un résumé de vidéo YouTube ?
R2:Le résumé d'une vidéo YouTube est un aperçu écrit du contenu d'une vidéo sur la plateforme YouTube. Le résumé permet de comprendre rapidement le sujet de la vidéo et les informations importantes.

Q3:Est-ce que YouTube Videos Summary Easy Copy avec ChatGPT est gratuit ?
R3:Bien que notre extension soit actuellement gratuite, nous étudions la possibilité d'introduire un petit paywall pour soutenir le service à l'avenir. En passant au service payant, vous bénéficierez de temps de réponse plus rapides, d'un accès illimité et d'un support client prioritaire. Notre objectif ultime est de vous fournir le meilleur service possible d'une manière abordable et accessible à tous.

Q4:Dois-je créer un compte ChatGPT/OpenAI pour utiliser cette extension ?
R4:Oui, vous devez avoir un compte ChatGPT pour utiliser cette extension. Vous pouvez créer un compte gratuit sur chat.openai.com.

ChatGPTとClaude3を使用してYouTube動画、ウェブ記事、およびPDFをワンクリックで要約し、インテリジェントにマインドマップを生成し、NoteGPT AIとチャットします。タイムスタンプとスクリーンショット付きのメモを記録します。任意のウェブページでテキストをハイライトし、最適な定義と翻訳を取得。重要な内容はソーシャルメディアに共有できます。

NoteGPT AIは、YouTube動画やウェブ記事（PDFの要約を含む）の要約と概要を提供し、ネット上のすべてのコンテンツを迅速に取得できるようにします。また、動画を視聴中にスクリーンショットを撮ったり、タイムスタンプ付きのメモを記録したりすることができ、時間を節約しながら迅速に学習できます。このツールはNoteGPT AIの能力を活用して、ウェブコンテンツから重要な情報を迅速に取得できます。PDFやその他の重要な内容をハイライトすることで、定義や翻訳を取得し、さらにインテリジェントなAIチャットも提供します。テキストをソーシャルメディアに共有することもサポートしています。

詳細は公式ウェブサイトをご覧ください：https://notegpt.io/、および機能ページ：https://notegpt.io/workspace/create。

🎉 主な特長：
● 時間の節約：1回のクリックでビデオのトランスクリプト内の特定のポイントを素早く検索できます。
● 洞察に富む：5秒間の迅速な概要のためにビデオの要約構造を自由に定義できます。
● ノートの強化：タイムスタンプ付きのインテリジェントなノートを記録し、スクリーンショットを簡単に撮影できます。
● AIチャット：NoteGPT AIにビデオコンテンツに関する難しい質問を投げかけ、深い回答を受け取ります。

● ウェブサマリー：1クリックでウェブページの概要を取得、ワード定義機能でキーポイントを把握。
● 思考マップ更新：構造化された知識の拡張のために編集可能な思考マップをスマートに生成
● AI 翻訳: 字幕と要約の本格的な翻訳にAIの能力を活用し、言語の制約を一切なくします。
● PDF要約：PDF要約ツールを使用してオンラインPDFやローカルPDFを要約し、効率的に知識を取得（arxiv論文を試してみる）
● 更新！！！ウェブハイライト：ウェブテキストのハイライト、オンラインPDFのハイライト、テキスト翻訳、定義と重要ポイントの表示、ハイライトしたテキストをTwitterに共有する機能をサポート

👉🏻 使い方：
【YouTubeビデオサマリー】
● YouTubeのウェブサイトを訪れます。
● 興味のあるビデオを選択します。
● ビデオのトランスクリプトを表示するために「Transcript」タブをクリックします。
● ビデオの概要をすばやく確認し、プロンプトをカスタマイズするために「Summary」タブに移動します。
● タイムスタンプの付いたビデオノートを記録するために「Notes」タブを訪れ、対応する位置にジャンプする能力を備えます。簡単にスクリーンショットを撮影します。
●「AI Chat」タブをクリックして、NoteGPT AIとのインテリジェントな対話に参加します。「Summary」ページの推奨された質問からこのページにアクセスします。

【ウェブ要約】
● 任意のウェブページ（オンラインPDFを含む）の右側にあるNoteGPT浮動アイコンをクリック
● ウェブページの要約を迅速に取得し、概要と関連するFAQを確認
● ウェブページやオンラインPDFから単語や段落をハイライトし、さらに詳細な定義、翻訳、ハイライトを表示し、重要な内容をワンクリックでTwitterに共有
● 設定ページでウェブ要約のオン/オフを自由に定義できます
【マインドマップ】
● Summaryページでワンクリックでマインドマップを生成
●  マウスでドラッグ、ズーム、縮小し、全方位で閲覧可能

●  効率的な編集で、迅速に作成、カスタマイズ、マインドマップをエクスポート
●  テキストを視覚的思考に変換し、あなたのアイデアを解放
● AIマインドマップをウォーターマークなしのPNG、SVGとしてダウンロード


💡 よくある質問：
● Q1: NoteGPTとは何ですか？
● A1: NoteGPTはさまざまな学習者向けに設計されたインテリジェントな学習アシスタントです。ビデオや記事を含む任意のウェブサイトから情報の要約と5秒の概要を提供します。AI駆動の要約、ノート、その他のAI機能で、あなたの時間の60%を節約することを目指しています。
● Q2：YouTube動画の要約とウェブ要約とは何ですか？
● A2：YouTube動画の要約は、YouTubeプラットフォーム上の動画内容の簡潔な概要です。ウェブ要約は、ウェブページ上のテキストの要点と概要を提供します（オンラインPDFも含む）。要約は、動画のテーマと重要な情報を迅速に理解する方法を提供します。
● Q3: NoteGPT: YouTubeとWebのサマリーをChatGPTで行うは無料ですか？
● A3: NoteGPT AIサービスは制限付きで無料です。15クォータを消費した後は、追加のクォータや安定性、迅速なサービス対応、個別のカスタマーサポートなどの特典が含まれる有料プランにアップグレードを検討してください。
● Q4: この拡張機能を使用するにはChatGPT/OpenAIアカウントを作成する必要がありますか？
● A4: ChatGPTアカウントは必要ありません。NoteGPTはChatGPTのアカウントなしで能力をシームレスに統合します。

NoteGPT AIを使用してYouTubeの学習体験を変えましょう！ 🚀

long.ko:
ChatGPT와 Claude3를 사용하여 YouTube 동영상, 웹 기사 및 PDF를 원클릭으로 요약하고, 지능적으로 마인드맵을 생성하며, NoteGPT AI와 채팅합니다. 타임스탬프와 스크린샷이 포함된 메모를 기록합니다. 어떤 웹 페이지에서든 텍스트를 하이라이트하여 최고의 정의와 번역을 얻으세요. 중요한 내용은 소셜 미디어에 공유할 수도 있습니다.

NoteGPT AI는 YouTube 동영상과 웹 기사(PDF 요약 포함)의 요약과 개요를 제공하여 인터넷상의 모든 콘텐츠를 빠르게 얻을 수 있도록 도와줍니다. 또한, 동영상을 시청하는 동안 빠르게 스크린샷을 찍거나 타임스탬프가 포함된 메모를 기록할 수 있어 시간을 절약하고 빠르게 학습할 수 있습니다. 이 도구는 NoteGPT AI 기능을 활용하여 웹 콘텐츠에서 중요한 정보를 빠르게 얻을 수 있습니다. PDF 또는 중요한 내용을 하이라이트하면 정의와 번역을 얻을 수 있으며, 지능형 AI 채팅도 제공합니다. 텍스트를 소셜 미디어에 공유하는 것도 지원합니다.

자세한 내용은 공식 웹 사이트를 방문하십시오: https://notegpt.io/및 기능 페이지에서 확인하십시오: https://notegpt.io/workspace/create。

🎉 주요 특징:
● 시간 절약: 한 번의 클릭으로 비디오 트랜스크립트에서 특정 지점을 빠르게 찾을 수 있습니다.
● 통찰력 있음: 5초 동안의 빠른 개요를 위해 비디오 요약 구조를 자유롭게 정의할 수 있습니다.
● 노트 강화: 타임 스탬프가 있는 지능적인 노트를 기록하고 쉽게 스크린샷을 찍을 수 있습니다.
● AI 챗: NoteGPT AI에게 동영상 내용에 관한 도전적인 질문을 하고 깊은 답변을 받을 수 있습니다.

● 생각지도 업데이트: 구조화된 지식 확장을 위한 편집 가능한 생각지도를 스마트하게 생성
●  AI 번역: 자막과 요약을 위한 AI 능력을 활용하여 진정한 번역을 실현하고 언어 장벽을 완전히 깨뜨립니다.
●  PDF 요약: PDF 요약기를 통해 온라인 PDF와 로컬 PDF를 요약하여 지식을 효율적으로 습득합니다.（arxiv 논문을 시도해보다）
●  NEW!!! 웹 하이라이팅: 웹 텍스트 하이라이팅, 온라인 PDF 하이라이팅, 텍스트 번역, 정의 및 주요 포인트 보기, 하이라이트된 텍스트를 트위터에 공유 지원

👉🏻 사용 방법:

【YouTube 비디오 요약】
● YouTube 웹사이트를 방문합니다.
● 관심 있는 동영상을 선택합니다.

ChatGPT with Youtube videos summary generator provides an access to the summary of YouTube videos. Let you quickly get the content of the YouTube video, save time and learn quicker. Relying on ChatGPT artificial intelligence, it will achieve effective re-creation.In addition,you can also easily copy information on both YouTube and chat.openai.com pages.

Features
● Save time:Quickly go to Youtube video location in the transcript
● Fast speed:Load quickly to videos summary
● Easy to use:Copy the transcript and summary with one click

How to use
● Simply go to YouTube website
● Choose the video you are interested in
● Click the Transcript &summary button.It will show you the video transcript, if it has.
● Click the View AI Summary Icon, If you already logged in chat.openai.com, we will get the video summary.
● Click the Copy Icon,then you easily get the summary of YT video.

🙋FAQ:
👉  Do you upgrade/modify the extension?
Yes, we do! In fact, at this very moment, we’re working on features that are probably going to be added. We have a goal of making ChatGPT for YouTube Video Summary the best ChatGPT extension out there, and we take this mission very seriously.We strive to keep up with the fast-paced development of ChatGPT to bring you the best possible experience.
👉  How do I install ChatGPT For YouTube in my browser ?
To install ChatGPT For YouTube on your browser, you will need to follow these steps:
1) In your browser open the browser's app store or extension store
2) Search for the ChatGPT For YouTube extension in the browser's app store or extension store (or click for : Google Chrome | Mozilla Firefox | edge)
3) Click on the "Add to Browser" or "Install" button to begin the installation process.
4) Follow the prompts to give the extension permission to access certain parts of your browser, if prompted.
👉  Are all of the features totally free to use?
Our extension is currently free and we are trying to always have one version of service that is free. But we would have to put in a small paywall in order to sustain the service. We have plans to do so in the coming weeks. With the paid service you can have faster service, without daily limits and high priority customer support. We aim to best serve you in a model that is most affordable to you.

long.pt_BR,pt_PT:
ChatGPT com gerador de resumo de vídeos do YouTube fornece acesso ao resumo de vídeos do YouTube. Permite que você obtenha rapidamente o conteúdo do vídeo do YouTube, economize tempo e aprenda mais rápido. Contando com a inteligência artificial do ChatGPT, ele obterá uma recriação eficaz.Além disso, Você também pode copiar informações facilmente nas páginas do YouTube e chat.openai.com.

Características
● Economize tempo: acesse rapidamente o local do vídeo do YouTube na transcrição
● Velocidade rápida: carregue rapidamente no resumo dos vídeos
● Fácil de usar: copie a transcrição e o resumo com um clique
● Suporte a chaves de API do ChatGPT: obtenha o resumo junto com os vídeos do Youtube diretamente.

Como usar
● Basta acessar o site do YouTube
● Escolha o vídeo de seu interesse
● Clique no botão Transcrição e resumo. Ele mostrará a transcrição do vídeo, se houver.
● Clique no ícone Exibir resumo do AI. Se você já estiver conectado ao chat.openai.com, obteremos o resumo do vídeo.
● Clique no ícone Copiar para obter facilmente o resumo do vídeo YT.

perguntas e respostas
Q1: O que é ChatGPT?
A1:ChatGPT é um modelo de linguagem desenvolvido pela OpenAI que utiliza uma grande rede neural baseada em Transformer pré-treinada para gerar texto semelhante ao humano em resposta às solicitações do usuário. Com sua ampla variedade de treinamento em texto da Internet, o ChatGPT pode fornecer respostas em vários tópicos, como conhecimentos gerais, conversas e escrita criativa.

Q2: O que é o resumo do vídeo do Youtube?
R2: O resumo do vídeo do YouTube é uma visão geral por escrito do conteúdo de um vídeo na plataforma do YouTube. O resumo fornece uma maneira rápida de entender o tópico do vídeo e as informações importantes.

P3: O resumo de vídeos do YouTube Easy Copy com ChatGPT é gratuito?
R3:Embora nossa extensão seja atualmente gratuita, estamos explorando a possibilidade de introduzir um pequeno paywall para sustentar o serviço no futuro. Ao atualizar para o serviço pago, você terá tempos de resposta mais rápidos, acesso irrestrito e suporte ao cliente de alta prioridade Nosso objetivo final é fornecer a você o melhor serviço possível de uma forma acessível a todos.

Q4: Preciso criar uma conta ChatGPT/OpenAI para usar esta extensão?
R4: Sim, você deve ter uma conta ChatGPT para usar esta extensão. Você pode criar uma conta gratuita em chat.openai.com.

● Fast speed:Load quickly to videos summary
● Easy to use:Copy the transcript and summary with one click

How to use
● Simply go to YouTube website
● Choose the video you are interested in
● Click the Transcript &summary button.It will show you the video transcript, if it has.
● Click the View AI Summary Icon, If you already logged in chat.openai.com, we will get the video summary.

A1:ChatGPT is an OpenAI-developed language model that utilizes a large pre-trained Transformer-based neural network to generate human-like text in response to user prompts. Q2:What is Youtube video summary?
A2:YouTube video summary is a written overview of the content in a video on the YouTube platform. The summary provides a quick way to understand the video's topic and important information.

By upgrading to the paid service, you will enjoy faster response times, unrestricted access, and high-priority customer support. Our ultimate goal is to provide you with the best possible service in a way that is affordable and accessible to everyone.

Q4:Do I need to create a ChatGPT/OpenAI account to use this extension?
A4:Yes, you must have a ChatGPT account to use this extension. You can create a free account at chat.openai.com.

💡問答
Q1：什麼是NoteGPT？
A1：NoteGPT 旨在成為各類學習者的智能學習助手。它允許您從任何網站獲取您想要的任何信息的摘要和 20 秒概述，包括影片和文章。通過人工智能驅動的摘要、筆記和其他人工智能功能，它旨在節省您 60% 的時間。NoteGPT嵌入ChatGPT的人工智能能力為您提供最聰明的服務。

Q2：什麼是YouTube影片摘要和網頁摘要？
A2：YouTube影片摘要是對YouTube平台上影片內容的簡要概述；網頁摘要是對網頁上的文字提供要點和概述。摘要提供了一種快速了解影片主題和重要信息的方法。

Q3：NoteGPT：YouTube影片和網頁摘要ChatGPT生成（中文版）免費嗎？
A3：NoteGPT AI 服務是免費的，但使用量有限。每個AI服務消耗一個配額。用完 15 個配額後，您需要升級到付費計劃以獲得更多配額。付費計劃還提供其他好處，例如更穩定、更快速的服務響應以及一對一的客戶支持。請訪問NoteGPT 的定價頁面（https://notegpt.io/pricing）了解更多信息。

Q4：我需要創建Chat GPT / OpenAI帳戶才能使用此擴展嗎？
A4：由於 NoteGPT 嵌入了 ChatGPT 的能力，因此您無需 ChatGPT 的帳戶即可使用此擴展。這將最大限度的解決您的
